Package: nutmod
Type: Package
Title: Modeling Nutrient Intake and Share of Requirements for Plausible Futures
Version: 0.1.0
Description: The Nutrient Modeling package provides tools to combine outputs
    from future scenarios using the IMPACT modelling environment. It uses GDP,
    population and gender and age distributions from the Shared Socioeconomic
    Profiles stored at IIASA, official values of Recommended Daily Allowances
    (RDAs) and Estimated Average Requirements (EAR), and expert assessments of the
    nutritional content of food items modeled in IMPACT.
Depends:
    R (> 3.2),
    data.table,
    openxlsx
